{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"（剧烈的喘息）","id":19,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"老爷子，快趴下！","id":21,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"去死吧！","id":23,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"什么？","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"没说你！是这只畜生......","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"快趴下，我的源石技艺马上就要爆炸了！","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#4$1","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"——！","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":32},{"type":"character","id":33},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_explo_n","id":34},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":35},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"false","id":36},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"0.93","g":"0.7","b":"0.2","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.93","g":"0.75","b":"0.32","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":39},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#6$1","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"我来拉您，没事吧？","id":41,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不用。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你手上的那是什么武器......那几头野兽瞬间被解决掉了......","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"我的独门狩猎绝技——就是用这个施术单元所施放的源石技艺，没人学得来。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"呵，小把戏而已。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"剩下的靠陷阱可以撑一会，后面就交给须本他们，我们可以去那边防御相对薄弱的地方......老爷子，您走慢点。","id":51,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不要废话。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"......","id":55,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你这是什么表情？","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":58},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"没事，只是有点怀念以前猎人们一起并肩作战的日子了。","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"而且，已经七年了，这是您第一次没有让我滚开，也没有骂我叛徒。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"我......没有想到您竟然真的会拿起......","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"明的狩猎矛，直说就好，我知道你是明的师父。没想到我会去杀那些野兽吗？","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"毕竟您当时不是猎人，也反对阿明来做猎人，阿明的牺牲......让您改变了很多。","id":67,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你知道就好。","id":69,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"......","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"老爷子，其实有件事......您也许一直有误解，这么多年，我......也不知道该如何向您开口。","id":73,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"当时并不是我没有救他......","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"诱兽粉。","id":77,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"啊？您知道？","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我可是他的父亲。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"这臭小子，他......是自己找死，就为了保护你们的矿场。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"直到现在，我还是常常梦见那天夜里他脸上的表情，他的动作，他的眼睛......","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"......到处是野兽的叫声，他最后想要对我说什么，但声音被淹没在喧嚣里，我还记得他苍白的嘴唇......","id":87,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"啊......","id":89,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"难道他是在说......","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":92},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":93},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":94},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":95},{"type":"Character","id":96},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"Background","image":"36_g3_redleafforest","screenadapt":"coverall","id":98},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"1","keep":"true","id":99},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$batmeeting_intro","key":"$batmeeting_loop","volume":"0.6","id":101,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"阿明！","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"*东国粗口*，怎么会有这么多野兽？你要做什么？","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"难道你对自己用了......","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"师父，你们回去，绝对不要跟上来！","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"你回来啊！我们可以在这里挡住它们！","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"不，师父！你比谁都清楚！","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"这等规模的兽潮不是我们可以击退的......很多人会受伤，甚至会有人牺牲。","id":115,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"源石矿场会被破坏，你们付出的所有心血都将会毁于一旦，我不能让这种事情发生。","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"明明你是最反对开矿场的不是吗？毁掉就毁掉了啊！","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"给我回来！没有什么比你活着更重要！","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"野兽都聚过来了。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"时间不多了，师父。","id":125,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"我反对矿场的开发，源石是危险的未知之物，一定会带来无法预估的灾难......","id":127,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"我也无法接受你们杀死那些无辜的生命。舍弃敬畏，放任贪婪，最终的结果只会是如此。","id":129,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"但是，我同样记得那天我们一起去到城市，看到的那些凭借源石而起的楼宇，那些耀眼的霓虹和闪亮的招牌......","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"源石是有价值的，它会帮助村子脱离现在困难的处境，能成为大家生存的依靠......已经走到了这一步，你们要好好地抓住这个机会。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"阿明！","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"猎人就是要为了族群的存续挺身而出，是你教我的，记得吗？","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"啊！滚开！你们这些畜生！不要再拦着我了！","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"兽潮，生命的愤怒。","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"我亦是为生存而面对它们，这是一场对等的战斗。","id":143,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"师父，最后答应我一件事。","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"啊......","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"今后，请带领大家......","id":149,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"活下去！","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"阿明！你回来！","id":153,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_760_1#1$1","id":154},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生明","text":"师父，最后一句话，请帮我转达给我的父亲，那个顽固的老头子。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":157},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":158},{"type":"Character","id":159},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":160},{"type":"Background","image":"36_g6_redleafforestB","screenadapt":"coverall","id":161},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.6","id":164,"musicid":2},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"他说的是......","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"“对不起，父亲。”","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"哼......你不用再编些话骗我了，他可从来没有喊过我父亲。","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"臭小子......","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"啊！","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"（深呼吸）","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"可是我啊......","id":177},{"type":"dialog","id":178},{"type":"character","id":179},{"type":"Text","text":"从这里看去只能看到老人的背影。","id":180},{"type":"Text","text":"但他听见了水珠落下的声音。","id":181},{"type":"Text","text":"深藏已久的泪水，盈满了纵横交错的沟壑。","id":182},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我很想他。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":185},{"type":"character","id":186},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":187},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_flapwing_2","volume":"0.2","id":188},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":189},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_flapwing_1","volume":"0.4","id":190},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":191},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"在天上！","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"是那头怪物......它果然来了。","id":195,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":196},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.6","id":197,"musicid":3},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"野兽又来了！*东国粗口*，怎么比之前多这么多？","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泷居应","text":"可恶，人手根本不够！","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_753_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你就在这里！布置刚刚那种陷阱，把野兽挡住！","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不许过去，让我去处理那家伙......","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我是猎人，那是我的猎物！","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":207},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"Character","id":210},{"type":"Background","image":"36_g2_easternvillageB","screenadapt":"showall","id":211},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":212},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":214},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_flapwing_2","volume":"0.8","id":216},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_flapwing_1","volume":"0.8","id":218},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_angervoice","volume":"0.5","id":220},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":221},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"夜刀！火龙来了！","id":223,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"果然还是来了。","id":225,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"因为我们之前激怒它太多次了，它将人类都视作了威胁。","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"它落在了柏生家附近，正在往这边靠近！","id":229,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#2$1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"支援......还要一段时间才能抵达，村民们还没有全到避难所。","id":231,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"偏偏选在这个时候......没办法了，你看着撤离的队伍，我去——","id":233,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1"},{"type":"character","id":234},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_snarl_2","volume":"1","id":236},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_snarl_1","volume":"1","id":237},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"夜刀！那边！有野兽出现了！数量在五只左右！","id":240,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"兽潮肯定到了，猎人们的封锁没办法完全抵挡所有来袭的野兽，必须优先保护眼前撤离的人群。","id":242,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#6$1","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"那怎么办？眼睁睁地看着火龙逼近吗？那只会是更糟糕的危机！","id":244,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"俺在想了......要找个办法阻挡火龙一段时间，至少等俺们把村民全部带过去......","id":246,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"柏生先生......","id":248,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"找柏生先生帮忙吗？可是一时找不到他，而且仅凭他一个人也......","id":250,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我看到他了，就在屋子旁边。","id":252,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#5$1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"他离火龙很近！夜刀，俺们是不是要......","id":254,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"如果他能够拖住火龙，我们就有时间去继续撤离村民了。","id":256,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑角","text":"夜刀，你是说......不去帮他？","id":258,"figure":"avg_1030_noirc2_1#9$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我们......只能相信他。","id":260,"figure":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"Character","id":263},{"type":"Background","image":"36_g2_easternvillageB","screenadapt":"showall","id":264},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":265},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":266},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","text":"","id":267},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_angervoice","volume":"0.5","id":268},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":269},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"（拧开油桶盖子）","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"嘿，你也觉得吧？今天真是个好日子，天空烧得亮堂堂的。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"最近发生了好多事，长大的女娃子回了村，闹得鸡犬不宁。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"突然有长着翅膀的怪物飞下来四处喷火，又来了两位不知好歹的外乡人在森林里惹麻烦。","id":276,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"后来野兽就一窝蜂地冲了出来，他们的矿场也爆炸了，不知道为什么就来了天灾，那些人连逃跑都乱成一团。","id":278,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"最可笑的是什么呢？从早到晚，又到早，老是有人跑过来，把过去那些烂在泥里的事挖出来，在我面前翻来覆去地讲。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"这些家伙啊，全都口口声声说着为我好，却用他们捡起来的过去，一片片地割开我的血肉。","id":282,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"还是黑角那娃子说的对，真相其实一点儿也不重要，过去就该让它留在过去。","id":284,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"死掉的人就让他死掉好了，一把火烧得干干净净，什么也别剩下。","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"Blocker","a":"